rows.label: qst720502_msg0001
rows.name:
Look, there's a bridge. I guess
that's Lett Bridge?

rows.label: qst720502_msg0003
rows.name: And they look rather tough to boot.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0004
rows.name:
You think? They don't look like
much to me.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, our analysis doesn't change the
facts - the bridge is blocked. We've
got to clear it.

rows.label: qst720502_msg0006
rows.name: Don't let your guard down, everyone!
